# Power BI Sales Dashboard

This project focuses on analyzing sales data and building an interactive dashboard using Power BI.

## Objectives
- Analyze sales performance
- Track KPIs like revenue, profit, and region performance
- Generate business insights

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- SQL (for data querying)
- Excel (dataset)

## Current Status
Project is under development. Initial analysis and data preparation in progress.

## Future Improvements
- Advanced KPI tracking
- Data cleaning using SQL
- Interactive dashboard design.


